  "description": {
    "en": "The General Statistics Office of Vietnam (GSO) is a government agency under the Ministry of Planning and Investment, responsible for state management of statistics and providing comprehensive social and economic information. GSO operates a vertical system with headquarters, 63 provincial statistical offices, and 713 district branch offices, serving over 5,300 employees nationwide.",
    "zh": "越南国家统计局（GSO）是隶属于计划与投资部的政府机构，负责国家统计管理职能，提供全面的社会经济信息。GSO采用垂直管理体系，包括总部、63个省级统计办公室和713个区级分支机构，在全国拥有超过5,300名员工。"
  },
